*&---------------------------------------------------------------------*
*& Report ZSTRING_REVERSE_641
*&---------------------------------------------------------------------*
*&
*&---------------------------------------------------------------------*
REPORT zstring_reverse_641.

PARAMETERS p1 TYPE string.
DATA p2 TYPE string.
PARAMETERS : times TYPE i .

TRANSLATE p1 TO LOWER CASE.

WRITE : 'Before String',p1.
ULINE.

p2 = reverse( p1 ).


WRITE : 'After Reverse String:',p2.
ULINE.

p2 = repeat( val = p1 occ = times ).

WRITE : 'After string Repeat :',p2.
